## 🔴 Critical Issues (Fix Immediately)

### 1. No robots.txt — Returns 404
- **Impact:** Search engines have no crawl directives; may crawl unnecessary pages or miss important ones
- **Fix:** Create `/public/robots.txt`:
```
User-agent: *
Allow: /
Disallow: /api/
Disallow: /_next/

Sitemap: https://innodify.in/sitemap.xml
```

### 2. No sitemap.xml — Returns 404
- **Impact:** Google cannot efficiently discover all your pages. Critical for a multi-page site with services, industries, case studies, and blog posts
- **Fix:** Install `next-sitemap` package:
```bash
npm install next-sitemap
```
Create `next-sitemap.config.js`:
```js
module.exports = {
  siteUrl: 'https://innodify.in',
  generateRobotsTxt: true,
  changefreq: 'weekly',
  priority: 0.7,
}
```

### 3. No Schema/JSON-LD Structured Data
- **Impact:** Missing Rich Results in Google Search entirely. No Organization, LocalBusiness, WebSite, BreadcrumbList, or Service schema detected
- **Fix:** Add JSON-LD to the homepage `<head>`:
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@graph": [
    {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "@id": "https://innodify.in/#organization",
      "name": "Innodify",
      "url": "https://innodify.in",
      "logo": "https://innodify.in/logo.png",
      "sameAs": [],
      "address": {
        "@type": "PostalAddress",
        "streetAddress": "6th Floor, 602 Sundram Plus, Timaliyawad, Athugar St",
        "addressLocality": "Surat",
        "addressRegion": "Gujarat",
        "postalCode": "395001",
        "addressCountry": "IN"
      },
      "contactPoint": {
        "@type": "ContactPoint",
        "telephone": "+91-79843-71199",
        "contactType": "sales",
        "availableLanguage": ["English", "Hindi"]
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "WebSite",
      "@id": "https://innodify.in/#website",
      "url": "https://innodify.in",
      "name": "Innodify",
      "publisher": { "@id": "https://innodify.in/#organization" }
    },
    {
      "@type": "WebPage",
      "@id": "https://innodify.in/#webpage",
      "url": "https://innodify.in",
      "name": "Innodify | Digital Solutions Agency",
      "isPartOf": { "@id": "https://innodify.in/#website" },
      "about": { "@id": "https://innodify.in/#organization" }
    }
  ]
}
```

### 4. No Canonical Tags
- **Impact:** Potential duplicate content issues (http/https, www/non-www, trailing slashes)
- **Fix:** Add to every page's `<head>`:
```html
<link rel="canonical" href="https://innodify.in/[current-page-path]" />
```
In Next.js, use the `metadata` export or `next/head`.

### 5. No Open Graph / Twitter Card Meta Tags
- **Impact:** When shared on LinkedIn, Twitter, WhatsApp — no branded preview image, title, or description appears. Critical for an agency that relies on social proof
- **Fix:** Add to each page:
```html
<meta property="og:title" content="Innodify | Digital Solutions Agency" />
<meta property="og:description" content="AI, CRM, SaaS, Web & Mobile Solutions" />
<meta property="og:image" content="https://innodify.in/og-image.jpg" />
<meta property="og:url" content="https://innodify.in/" />
<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
<meta name="twitter:title" content="Innodify | Digital Solutions Agency" />
<meta name="twitter:description" content="AI, CRM, SaaS, Web & Mobile Solutions" />
<meta name="twitter:image" content="https://innodify.in/og-image.jpg" />
```

### 6. Security Headers — 6 of 7 Missing

| Header | Status |
|--------|--------|
| Strict-Transport-Security (HSTS) | ❌ MISSING |
| Content-Security-Policy | ✅ `upgrade-insecure-requests` (partial) |
| X-Frame-Options | ❌ MISSING |
| X-Content-Type-Options | ❌ MISSING |
| X-XSS-Protection | ❌ MISSING |
| Referrer-Policy | ❌ MISSING |
| Permissions-Policy | ❌ MISSING |

- **Impact:** Security is a Trust signal for E-E-A-T. Missing HSTS allows downgrade attacks. Google uses HTTPS as a ranking factor
- **Fix:** Add headers in `next.config.js`:
```js
async headers() {
  return [{
    source: '/(.*)',
    headers: [
      { key: 'Strict-Transport-Security', value: 'max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload' },
      { key: 'X-Frame-Options', value: 'SAMEORIGIN' },
      { key: 'X-Content-Type-Options', value: 'nosniff' },
      { key: 'Referrer-Policy', value: 'strict-origin-when-cross-origin' },
      { key: 'Permissions-Policy', value: 'camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()' },
    ],
  }];
}
```

