## 🟠 High Priority (Fix Within 1 Week)

### 7. Duplicate Page Title — "Innodify | Digital Solutions Agency"
- **Finding:** Homepage and About page both have the same `<title>` tag
- **Impact:** Google may struggle to differentiate pages; reduces CTR from SERPs
- **Fix:** Each page needs a unique, descriptive title (30-60 characters):
  - Homepage: `Innodify | AI, Web & Mobile Development Agency in Surat`
  - About: `About Innodify | Meet Our Team & Our Story`
  - Services: `Our Services | Web, Mobile, AI & eCommerce Solutions`

### 8. Thin Content on About Page
- **Finding:** About page has ~200 words of unique content (below 400 word minimum)
- **Missing:** Co-founder bios have no credentials, qualifications, or background
- **Impact:** Weak E-E-A-T signals — Google needs to see expertise and experience
- **Fix:**
  - Add detailed founder bios (50-100 words each with credentials)
  - Add company history, founding story, mission statement detail
  - Include verifiable metrics ("delivered 100+ projects" with specifics)

### 9. No Blog Post Dates or Author Attribution
- **Finding:** Blog listing page shows 9 posts but no publication dates, no authors
- **Impact:** Google's December 2025 core update penalizes anonymous content even for non-YMYL. E-E-A-T now applies to ALL competitive queries
- **Fix:** Add author bylines with bios and visible publication/update dates

### 10. Navigation Points to Self on Non-JS Load
- **Finding:** When JavaScript doesn't load, nav links for "Services", "Industries", "Company", "Resources" all `href` to the current page URL instead of a fallback
- **Impact:** Bots that don't execute JS see broken navigation; links don't pass PageRank properly
- **Fix:** Set the `href` to proper fallback URLs (e.g., `/services`, `/industries`)

---

## 🟡 Medium Priority (Fix Within 1 Month)

### 11. Service Pages — Light on Content
- **Finding:** AI Solutions page has ~250 words (below 800 word minimum for service pages)
- **Impact:** Unlikely to rank for competitive terms like "AI development agency" or "custom AI solutions"
- **Fix:** Expand each service page to 800+ words with:
  - Detailed process descriptions
  - Technology stack details
  - Client results / case study snippets
  - Pricing context or engagement models

### 12. No BreadcrumbList Schema
- **Impact:** Missing breadcrumb rich results in Google
- **Fix:** Add `BreadcrumbList` JSON-LD on all inner pages

### 13. Missing Service Schema
- **Fix:** Add `Service` schema for each service page with provider, service type, area served

### 14. No `hreflang` Tags
- **Finding:** Site targets India but has no language declaration beyond the HTML `lang` attribute
- **Impact:** Minor for single-language sites but could improve clarity for Google

### 15. Footer Links Duplicated
- **Finding:** Footer service links appear twice (once in list, once as separate links)
- **Impact:** Dilutes link equity, confusing for crawlers

---

## 🟢 Low Priority (Backlog)

### 16. No llms.txt for AI Crawlers
- **Impact:** AI search engines (ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude) have no guidance on citing your content

### 17. Consider Adding a Case Study Schema
- Use `CreativeWork` or `Article` schema on case study pages

### 18. Newsletter Form — No CTA Optimization
- The newsletter subscribe section has no value proposition or incentive

