## E-E-A-T Assessment: 35/100 🔴

| Factor | Weight | Score | Assessment |
|--------|--------|-------|-----------|
| Experience | 20% | 40 | Case studies show real work, but lack specific metrics and first-person narrative |
| Expertise | 25% | 30 | No author credentials, no certifications shown, no team bios with qualifications |
| Authoritativeness | 25% | 25 | Claims "Award Winning" but no awards listed; no external validation visible |
| Trustworthiness | 30% | 45 | Good: contact info, address, phone. Bad: missing security headers, no reviews/testimonials on homepage |

### Key E-E-A-T Improvements:
1. Add **detailed founder bios** with qualifications, certifications, years of experience
2. Show **specific project metrics** in case studies (traffic increases, conversion rates, timelines)
3. **List awards/certifications** with links (Google Partner, AWS, etc.)
4. Add **client testimonials** with names and companies
5. Add **team page** with individual expertise areas

