## Performance (Estimated from Source): 60/100

> ⚠️ PageSpeed Insights API not enabled on your Google Cloud project. Scores estimated from source code analysis.

| Signal | Finding |
|--------|---------|
| Framework | Next.js (SSR/ISR) ✅ |
| Compression | Brotli ✅ |
| CDN | Hostinger hCDN ✅ |
| Cache-Control | `s-maxage=31536000` ✅ |
| Image optimization | Next.js Image component likely used ✅ |
| JavaScript bundle | Potential concern — heavy animations visible |
| Server | `X-Powered-By: Next.js` exposed (minor security info leak) |
| TTFB | CDN cache HIT detected — likely fast ✅ |

### Potential CWV Concerns:
- Heavy hero animations could impact **LCP** and **INP**
- Ensure images have explicit `width`/`height` to avoid **CLS**
- Remove `X-Powered-By` header for security

